<p><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200921/6fca725472c346d1b8b42b13cb1cc437.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span>图片来源：英特尔</span></p>
<blockquote>
<p><span>记者 | </span><span>彭新</span></p>
